{"tid":1616943,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[YOHO戒嚴] 防暴警察指在商場內的市民非法集結","createTime":"2019-10-03T14:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T15:24:11.000Z","uid":231583,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0ec0b5de8fc65a8d15bbfe137e64ff8393c03441","tid":1616943,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:56:55.000Z","msg":"2248 #元朗 #元朗站 #yoho <br />\n大批防暴警察在元朗站戒備，較早時防暴警察指在商場內的市民非法集結。<br />\n#now<br />\n<br />\n幾時申請埋禁制令，要消費後先可以離開商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b91d492a1ba7269a66ff32fb8fc9fe247351898","tid":1616943,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:57:19.000Z","msg":"#請廣傳 <br />\n<br />\n香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會聽日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=a70ca2c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"9312f8aee3b9ad8158203180826442dcb043d0fe","tid":1616943,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:58:35.000Z","msg":"元朗人快d搞死YOHO<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經濟戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97e885e556b9d5960e2991e39a747062d7530f3","tid":1616943,"uid":56518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:00:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n今日開始再無&ldq